name: Sun Ball
description:
The sun is the centre of life emits all colours of the rainbow.
By amplifying the rayed light, this series gives space to the colours of the sun and let you decide on the mood. 
PNG, 3600 × 2700, 300 dpi

Part of the "In the mood of Sun" Series:
- When the Dark is gone (Iran)
- Saigon Haze (Vietnam)
- Sun Ball (Indonesia)
